Class Client

  • java.lang.Object
    • ocsf.client.AbstractClient
      • client.Client
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IScreenController, java.lang.Runnable

    public class Client
extends ocsf.client.AbstractClient
implements IScreenController
    The main connector between the user interface and the server. This class sends user requests to the server and handles the returned values from the server.
